N
N=\inf \{ n ; S_n>0 \}
A \subset \mathbf R
 U = \mathbf{E} \left[ \sum_{n \geq N} \mathbf{1}_A (S_n) \right] = \mathbf{E} \left[ \sum_{n \geq N} \mathbf{1}_{A-S_N} (S_n-S_N) \right] 
S_n-S_N
S_{n-N}
n \geq N
a
\mu(a)=\mathbf{E}\left[ \sum_{n \geq 0} \mathbf{1}_{A-a} (S_n) \right]
 U = \mathbf{E} [\mu(S_N)]
